data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom garden level  ranch home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. The heart of the home is the beautifully designed kitchen, featuring modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. The primary bedroom offers a private oasis with an on-suite bathroom. The additional two bedrooms are equally spacious and bathed in natural light, Step outside to the sprawling deck overlooking the  backyard and discover your own piece of paradise. The outdoor space is perfect and ready to make it your own. Located in the sought-after Promontory subdivision, this home offers easy access to a plethora of amenities. Take a leisurely stroll to nearby parks, enjoy shopping and dining options just a short drive away, and benefit from proximity to excellent schools. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and allure of this wonderful property in person! Motivated seller. Rate buy down with preferred lender.
